        <scope>This topic handles all employee issues and service requests related to software applications, system access, and user accounts. This includes installing, configuring, and troubleshooting software applications, as well as managing permissions and licenses. 

This topic includes, but is not limited to:

Software Issues &amp; Errors: &apos;Report Software Issue&apos; (e.g., &apos;Slack is crashing,&apos; &apos;Salesforce is frozen,&apos; &apos;I&apos;m getting an error in Workday,&apos; &apos;Outlook won&apos;t open&apos;).

Software Lifecycle &amp; Installation: &apos;Request Software Installation,&apos; &apos;Request Software Uninstallation,&apos; &apos;New Software Evaluation Request,&apos; &apos;Operating System Reinstallation,&apos; &apos;Request Software Update&apos; (e.g., &apos;How do I update my browser?&apos;).

Access, Accounts, &amp; Collaboration: &apos;Request Software Access&apos; (e.g., &apos;I can&apos;t log into Salesforce,&apos; &apos;I need access to a shared drive&apos;), &apos;Request New License&apos; (e.g., &apos;I need Adobe Photoshop&apos;), &apos;New Email Account,&apos; &apos;Create a New Collaboration Space (e.g., Teams Channel, Slack Channel),&apos; &apos;Add to Group&apos; (e.g., &apos;Please add me to the &quot;Marketing&quot; email group&apos;).

Application Passwords: &apos;Reset Application Password&apos; (e.g., &apos;I need to reset my password for Concur,&apos; not your main computer password).</scope>
        <source>svc_emp_intelligence__SoftwareManagement</source>
