        <scope>This topic handles all employee issues and service requests related to physical IT equipment and user-assigned devices. This includes the procurement, setup, repair, and replacement of all computer hardware and peripherals.

This topic includes, but is not limited to:

New Hardware &amp; Lifecycle Requests: &apos;Request New Hardware (Laptop, Monitor, etc.),&apos; &apos;Request Laptop Replacement,&apos; &apos;Device Return Request&apos; (e.g., offboarding, equipment return).

Peripherals &amp; Upgrades: &apos;Request a Peripheral (Keyboard, Mouse, Docking Station),&apos; &apos;Hardware Upgrade Request (RAM, SSD)&apos;

Device Setup &amp; Security Configuration: &apos;Enroll Device for MDM&apos; (Mobile Device Management), &apos;Device Encryption Setup/Verification/Issue&apos;

Printer &amp; Supplies Management: &apos;Report Printer Issue&apos; (e.g., &apos;Printer is jammed,&apos; &apos;Can&apos;t connect&apos;), &apos;Request Printer Supplies (Paper, Cartridge)&apos;

Display &amp; Presentation Support: &apos;Projector/Display Setup &amp; Support&apos; (e.g., &apos;Can&apos;t connect to the projector,&apos; &apos;Conference room display issue&apos;).

General Break-Fix &amp; Support: &apos;Report Device Issue&apos; (e.g., &apos;My laptop is slow,&apos; &apos;My computer won&apos;t turn on,&apos; &apos;My phone screen is cracked,&apos; &apos;My monitor is flickering,&apos; &apos;My dock isn&apos;t working&apos;).

Current Assigned Assets: &apos;What assets are assigned to me?,&apos; &apos;Show my assigned devices,&apos; &apos;What equipment do I have?,&apos; &apos;List my hardware,&apos; &apos;Can you get details on my monitor?,&apos; &apos;Tell me about my laptop,&apos; &apos;Which devices are allocated to me?&apos;

If its not in above strictly do not run this topic.</scope>
        <source>svc_emp_intelligence__HardwareManagement</source>
