        <pluginType>Topic</pluginType>
        <scope>This topic handles all employee issues and service requests related to the physical office environment, building services, and on-site amenities. This includes all non-IT physical assets managed by the workplace team.

This topic includes, but is not limited to:

Building Maintenance &amp; Environment: &apos;Report Building Maintenance Issue&apos; (e.g., lights out, water spill, broken door), &apos;Adjust AC Temperature&apos; (e.g., &apos;It&apos;s too cold at my desk,&apos; &apos;The heat is too high&apos;), &apos;Request Housekeeping/Cleaning Support&apos; (e.g., &apos;The restroom needs cleaning,&apos; &apos;Request a carpet cleaning&apos;).

Furniture &amp; Office Moves: &apos;Office Move IT Support&apos; (e.g., &apos;I am moving desks and need my equipment moved&apos;), &apos;Request Minor Furniture Moves&apos; (e.g., &apos;I need to move a whiteboard,&apos; &apos;Help moving a cabinet&apos;), &apos;Report Broken Furniture&apos; (e.g., &apos;My chair is broken&apos;), &apos;Request Ergonomic Equipment&apos; (e.g., &apos;I need a standing desk&apos;).

Physical Access &amp; Security: &apos;New ID (Badge) request,&apos; &apos;Report Lost Badge&apos; (e.g., &apos;My access badge isn&apos;t working,&apos; &apos;I lost my keycard&apos;), &apos;Register a Guest.&apos;

Office Supplies &amp; Amenities: &apos;Request Office Supplies (Markers, Duster, Sticky Notes),&apos; &apos;Report Amenity Issue&apos; (e.g., &apos;The coffee machine is broken,&apos; &apos;We are out of snacks in the kitchen&apos;).

Conference Rooms &amp; Spaces: &apos;Conference Room Reservation&apos; (e.g., &apos;I need to book the Banyan room&apos;), &apos;Report Room Issue&apos; (e.g., &apos;The monitor in &apos;Room 101&apos; is broken,&apos; &apos;There are no markers&apos;).</scope>
        <source>svc_emp_intelligence__FacilitiesManagement</source>
